node.title: Judge reserves decision on Brian Tamaki's bail appeal
node.description: The Destiny Church leader has been in Mount Eden Prison for 10 days.
node.content: ["The judge presiding over the bail appeal for Brian Tamaki has reserved his decision.", "The Destiny Church leader has been in Mount Eden Prison for 10 days after being arrested for breaching bail conditions by speaking at an anti-vaccine rally.", "He is due to appear before the Auckland District Court tomorrow over the charges.", "Protesters had currently gathered outside the prison in support of Tamaki.", "This is breaking news - more to come.", "RNZ"]
